{"tid":2152174,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA GeForce RTX 30 或快推出，官方預告片洩露玄機","createTime":"2020-08-11T22:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T22:09:45.000Z","uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f09bf44ec62b030abebf12c14a0396801a482ab3","tid":2152174,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T22:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76JWigZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76JWigZ.jpg&h=66fed3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半導體公司 NVIDIA 昨日（10 日）在其官方 Twitter 和 Facebook 等社文平台上發布了一則廣告，疑似透露 GeForce RTX 30 &ldquo;Ampere&rdquo; 遊戲顯示卡（Display Card）的推出日期。<br />\n <br />\nNVIDIA 昨日在其官方 Twitter &ldquo;Ultimate Countdown&rdquo; 發布了一則預告短片，影片中不全長不足 10 秒，而畫面亦只見疑似外太空的地方發生爆炸，除標上 #ULTIMATE COUNTDOWN 字樣外，並未有多加描述。<br />\n<br />\n不過，再配合 GeForce 官方 Twitter 的個人封面圖片 &ldquo;21 DAYS. 21 YEARS&rdquo; 推測，21 年前為 1999 年，NVIDIA 發布 GeForce 256 的時間，而 21 天則是此預告發布後的 21 日，即 8 月 31 日，故外界推斷 NVIDIA 或在暗示當日將會宣布有關 GeForce 的信息，而很大可能會是 GeForce RTX 30 &ldquo;Ampere&rdquo; 遊戲顯示卡的發布。<br />\n<br />\n雖然以上皆為推斷，但仍然可以期待一下 8 月 31 日，NVIDIA 會否真的發布新顯示卡。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：Nvidia"},{"pid":"bd600ca20388e0a2dcd206589d54324d04bc6bee","tid":2152174,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T22:43:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nvidiageforce/status/1292808003897311232?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnvidiageforce%2Fstatus%2F1292808003897311232%3Fs%3D21&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=6690b347\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnvidiageforce%2Fstatus%2F1292808003897311232%3Fs%3D21&h=2bf4a111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nvidiageforce/status/1292808003897311232?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n預告片link"},{"pid":"44c877245fde34a3e4b41d5c4db9620af39687d6","tid":2152174,"uid":126835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT